Global Intelligent Meeting Management System Market Insights
Intelligent Meeting Management System Market size was valued at USD 2.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 6.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 16.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Intelligent Meeting Management System Market Overview
The global Intelligent Meeting Management System market has seen substantial growth, valued at approximately $4.7 billion in 2024. This sector is expected to grow at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 16.2% from 2024 to 2030, reaching a projected value of $12.6 billion by 2030. The increasing adoption of AI-driven solutions, cloud-based technologies, and the rise of remote and hybrid work environments are the main contributors to this market expansion. These systems are increasingly being adopted by organizations for more efficient and effective meeting management, improving productivity, and reducing time and resource wastage.

